{"tid":2426391,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"想要處女係一個擇偶條件","createTime":"2021-02-28T05:24:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-28T12:07:16.000Z","uid":201182,"like":7,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"70d2ae0aa41fc3a64a7c6e37358664b17051eb40","tid":2426391,"uid":201182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T05:24:51.000Z","msg":"有d人想要處女做女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,佢地就會將成件事比喻為同''女人想揀有錢男人''一樣,都只係一個擇偶條件<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁通常係呢個時候,就會有人出黎反問番個男方<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,問佢係咪處男<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,而當佢唔係處男既時候,就會追問,問佢憑咩要求女方係處女<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />     <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:自己唔係處就唔應該求女方係處女<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果係咁的話,想要靚仔做男朋友既女人係咪要一樣咁靚女;想嫁有錢仔既女人係咪要一樣咁有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/mask.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63eb9b5a01a92f541449cfac14b75a12c7636df0","tid":2426391,"uid":177089,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T05:41:31.000Z","msg":"1999 樓主真絲confirmed"},{"pid":"4a98a4a1b3eaf603a10baf424db92defc7866b4a","tid":2426391,"uid":343770,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T10:23:04.000Z","msg":"處男先最重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60f967cb1d2a4c9788499fb7bfde37517922dba4","tid":2426391,"uid":69168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T10:29:11.000Z","msg":"所以話啲比喻真係on99，一句話唔想要二手閪咪算，<br />\n有閪冇閪呢啲天生，男女本來就唔係平等，<br />\n企喺道德高地解釋咁多只會越辯越柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c89c678e3b7eef4fe8b90905e4843a2c0554764","tid":2426391,"uid":62841,"like"